attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Newly constructed in 2020, this attached single family offers three bedrooms, three full bathrooms, finished lower level, huge turf backyard and approx. 1,590 SF of living space. The main floor features a stunning chef's kitchen with full sized Thermador refrigerator and Wolf range, oversized wet bar with wine fridge and living room and access to a deck for grilling. The second floor consists of two generously sized bedrooms perfect for guests or an office, laundry room and shared full bathroom. The primary en-suite makes up the whole top floor, with a walk out roof deck with incredible city views! The lower level offers another large living room area/home office and full bathroom with direct access to the turf fenced in backyard. Additional features include hardwood floors throughout, Sonos speakers, central AC/heat, quartz counters, located just steps to Broadway's shops and restaurants!
